      <lg n="1" type="stanza"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-M12171H1-line-1"><hi rend="display-initial">T</hi>HE Rose's age is but a day;</l><l n="2" xml:id="spp-M12171H1-line-2"> Its bloom the pledge of its decay:</l><l n="3" xml:id="spp-M12171H1-line-3"> Sweet in scent; in colour bright;</l><l n="4" xml:id="spp-M12171H1-line-4"> It blows at morn, and fades at night.M12171H1   </l></lg></div>
